WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Alhamdu Lillahi Rabbil Alamin

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Ar-Rahman Ar-Rahim

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Maliki Yawm Al-Din

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Iyyaka Na'budu Wa Iyyaka Nasta'iin

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Ihdina Siraka Al-Mustaqeem

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:21.000
Siraka Al-Laleen An'Anta Alayhim

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Ghayri Al-Mawdhubi Alayhim Walabdaam

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.400
Assalamu Alaikum Warahmatullahi Wabarakatuh

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:37.400
Bismillah Ar-Rahman Ar-Rahim

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:39.400
Alhamdu Lillahi Rabbil Alamin

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:41.400
Wa bihi Nasta'iin

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:43.400
Wa nusalli wa nusallimu ala afzalil khalqi ajmaeen

00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:45.400
Nabi'ina wa habibina Muhammadin

00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:47.400
Wa ala alihi wa ashabihi wa attabi'ina

00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:49.400
Wa man tabi'ahun bi ihsanin ila yawm al-Din wa ba'd

00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:51.400
We praise Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:55.400
We send blessings and salutations upon Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:59.400
May Allah bless him and all his household, his companions

00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:03.400
All those who have struggled and strived to protect the Deen

00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:07.400
From the very beginning in a way that today it has got to us

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:11.400
And may Allah make us from amongst those who can preserve it

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:13.400
And who can teach it to our children and others

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:17.400
In a way that inshallah our offspring will be protected and guarded

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:21.400
And in a way that we can be used for the pleasure of the Almighty

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:23.400
Rather than in the transgression of the Almighty

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:25.400
Ameen

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:27.400
Beloved brothers and sisters

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:29.400
This evening we will require a lot of concentration

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:35.400
Because we are going through one of the most important incidents that occurred in the history of Islam

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:45.400
And this is the first major battle that took place between the Muslims and those who had oppressed them for so many years

00:01:45.400 --> 00:01:55.400
And as we had said from the moment of revelation 14 years later to the day is when the battle of Badr took place

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:59.400
So if we say revelation was on the 17th of Ramadhan

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:01.400
We find this the 17th of Ramadhan

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:03.400
The battle of Badr took place

00:02:03.400 --> 00:02:05.400
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us protection

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:08.400
Remember, oppression will not last forever

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:11.400
Those who oppress one day they will have to pay

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:17.400
And one day they will be within the clutches of the same people whom they have oppressed

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:21.400
And this is the sunnah, this is the system of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:23.400
May Allah protect us from oppression

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:29.400
And may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala make us from amongst those who can be concerned about our own weaknesses

00:02:29.400 --> 00:02:36.400
And if we want to concern in the lives of others it should be how to uplift them rather than how to drop them

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:39.400
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:43.400
As we had made mention of there was the battle of the Al-Ashirah

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:47.400
Where the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam had heard that Abu Sufyan

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:52.400
Who was one of the leaders of Quraysh had taken a lot of the wealth of Quraysh

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:56.400
The wealth of the Muslims as well who had left Makkah al-Mukarramah

00:02:56.400 --> 00:03:03.400
There was a time when the Kuffar of Quraysh had usurped the wealth of the Muslims

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:07.400
And anything that they left behind they put it together, they made up these caravans

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:12.400
And they went in order to deal with the people in Ash-Sham or the Syrian region

00:03:12.400 --> 00:03:18.400
Which includes Syria, Lebanon, Palestine, that entire region in the northern part of the Arabian peninsula

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:23.400
So when the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam heard of this he went out with many of his companions

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:29.400
And they tried to get hold of the caravan of Abu Sufyan

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:33.400
And they only found that they had missed it and it had gone up already

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:38.400
So he returned to Madinah Munawwarah after some time and he started planning

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:41.400
And the planning was from Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:46.400
Because Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala had already informed Muhammad salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:51.400
We will grant you victory, we will grant you one of the two victories

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:55.400
So either you will have the caravan or you will be victorious over Quraysh

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:58.400
This was a promise by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:03.400
So what had happened amazingly, it was a blessing that that caravan had passed

00:04:03.400 --> 00:04:09.400
After some time the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam went to one or two other places with a few of his men

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:16.400
And the Sahaba were not made aware of the fact that an army was being prepared

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:19.400
To get the same caravan on its way back

00:04:19.400 --> 00:04:21.400
They were not told the details

00:04:21.400 --> 00:04:28.400
And this was one of the beauties of Rasulullah salallahu alaihi wasallam's system and style which was divine

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:30.400
Given by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:37.400
He did not used to inform the people of the details because it would be very easy for people to find out

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:41.400
If I were to keep it within myself, I know no one knows

00:04:41.400 --> 00:04:46.400
The minute I trust a person with it, perhaps many others would know

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:49.400
Well nowadays we have a sickness, you know when someone tells you something

00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:54.400
When you really want the news to fly, tell them don't tell anyone

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:59.400
That little statement don't tell anyone, what it does is it makes us itch to tell someone

00:04:59.400 --> 00:05:03.400
And when we tell someone we have a password, what's the password?

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:05.400
Don't tell anyone and then we tell them

00:05:05.400 --> 00:05:09.400
And they go and tell the whole world knows and everyone is saying don't tell anyone

00:05:09.400 --> 00:05:12.400
But may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala safeguard us

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:14.400
Look at how we have degenerated

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:18.400
The best thing if you don't want people to know, do not tell anyone

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:22.400
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness and may He grant us a lesson

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:26.400
So Rasulullah salallahu alaihi wasallam began to prepare

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:29.400
And as they left Al Madinah Al Munawarah

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:35.400
They were 313 men according to the majority of narrations

00:05:35.400 --> 00:05:40.400
Some take it a little bit higher to 340 and some drop it to 311

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:44.400
We would stick to the narration that is most common, 313 men

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:47.400
The Rasulullah salallahu alaihi wasallam went with them

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:51.400
Now one might ask why is there discrepancy in the figure, it's very simple

00:05:51.400 --> 00:05:56.400
Because when they initially went they were quite a few, they were perhaps up to 340

00:05:56.400 --> 00:06:00.400
But when the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam got to a place

00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:04.400
Known as Baytu Suqiyah just outside Madinah Al Munawarah

00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:07.400
He stopped and the army camped there for a while

00:06:07.400 --> 00:06:11.400
And as we mentioned yesterday he vetted the people one by one

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:16.400
And he sent people back to Madinah Al Munawarah who were not fit to join him

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:21.400
Because they were too young perhaps or because they had other duties in Madinah

00:06:21.400 --> 00:06:25.400
Or because he wanted them to fulfill something in Madinah Al Munawarah

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:30.400
The example we cited was that of Uthman ibn Affan radiallahu anhu

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:33.400
He wanted to go out, the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam told him

00:06:33.400 --> 00:06:38.400
Your wife is ill and sick, Ruqayya binti Rasul salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:45.400
She is not well, you go back and you will have a full reward of every one of us that goes out

00:06:45.400 --> 00:06:48.400
And on top of that whatever the outcome is

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:54.400
You will be granted a full status of a person who took part in whatever we are going to take part in

00:06:54.400 --> 00:06:58.400
And this is why if you open the Sahih of Imam Al-Bukhari

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:01.400
And you find the names which are written of the people of Badr

00:07:01.400 --> 00:07:04.400
He makes mention of Uthman ibn Affan radiallahu anhu

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:06.400
Although physically he was not there

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:10.400
That is because he was told that you will be considered as one of them, subhanallah

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:13.400
So this we learn a great lesson from

00:07:13.400 --> 00:07:19.400
Because we need to realize that sometimes there are certain things we have to take care of

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:23.400
At that time it was not compulsory for them to have come out

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:27.400
Because the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam made a voluntary announcement

00:07:27.400 --> 00:07:31.400
Whoever wants to come out with us, we have this something we would like to do inshallah

00:07:31.400 --> 00:07:36.400
And so on, they knew that they went out on escapades, little platoons, little reconnaissance missions

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:40.400
As we made mention of to gather a little bit of intelligence and so on

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:45.400
So had they known that it was going to end in a full-fledged battle

00:07:45.400 --> 00:07:49.400
There would have been no body or very few in Madinah Munawwarah

00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:51.400
But Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala's plan

00:07:52.400 --> 00:07:54.400
So these 313 they had left

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:57.400
When they left they got to a certain point as we said

00:07:57.400 --> 00:08:00.400
And this was a place known as Bayt al-Suqya

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:02.400
Just outside Madinah Munawwarah

00:08:02.400 --> 00:08:06.400
As they camped there the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam sent two men

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:09.400
Go and find out how far these people are

00:08:09.400 --> 00:08:14.400
Who? The caravan of Abu Sufyan returning from Ash-Sham

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:18.400
So the two who were Talhah ibn Ubaydi Allah radiallahu anhu

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:21.400
And Sa'id ibn Zaid radiallahu anhu

00:08:21.400 --> 00:08:25.400
These two, they had gone out and they saw this caravan

00:08:25.400 --> 00:08:29.400
They sent back a message to Muhammad salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:08:29.400 --> 00:08:34.400
But Abu Sufyan had seen them and Quraysh was already very wary

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:38.400
Because they had had previous caravans where they had skirmishes with the Muslims

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:41.400
We made mention of them, this was not the first time

00:08:41.400 --> 00:08:43.400
They were worried, they were concerned

00:08:43.400 --> 00:08:46.400
And Abu Sufyan was extremely intelligent

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:48.400
A very very wise young man

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:50.400
Not as old as Abu Jahal and the others

00:08:50.400 --> 00:08:54.400
He was wise, very intelligent

00:08:54.400 --> 00:08:59.400
What he did is he understood that there are people spying here on us

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:03.400
And he realized that these people are from Madinah

00:09:03.400 --> 00:09:04.400
How did he pick it up?

00:09:04.400 --> 00:09:07.400
Look at the narrations, the intelligence of these people

00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:09.400
Very sharp people

00:09:09.400 --> 00:09:11.400
He looked at the droppings of the camel

00:09:11.400 --> 00:09:14.400
And he studied the droppings of the camel

00:09:14.400 --> 00:09:21.400
And he saw in it that the fodder that these camels have been fed with is only from Madinah

00:09:21.400 --> 00:09:23.400
Cannot be from anywhere else, amazing

00:09:23.400 --> 00:09:27.400
Because they had in it some of whatever was only in Madinah

00:09:27.400 --> 00:09:31.400
The produce, the leaves of the palm and so on

00:09:31.400 --> 00:09:33.400
Which you could not find anywhere else

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:34.400
Intelligent man

00:09:34.400 --> 00:09:36.400
And he knew that now there is a problem

00:09:36.400 --> 00:09:39.400
So what he did was also

00:09:39.400 --> 00:09:40.400
He began

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:43.400
The first thing that he started to do was

00:09:43.400 --> 00:09:46.400
He told his people, we are very few in number

00:09:46.400 --> 00:09:48.400
The best bet is to change our path

00:09:48.400 --> 00:09:49.400
We change the road

00:09:49.400 --> 00:09:51.400
So instead of going close to Madinah

00:09:51.400 --> 00:09:55.400
And as we are passing we will, you know, use the normal road

00:09:55.400 --> 00:09:58.400
We rather go on the difficult road

00:09:58.400 --> 00:10:02.400
And the further road which is closer to the coast

00:10:02.400 --> 00:10:05.400
So by that time no one will be able to get to us

00:10:05.400 --> 00:10:07.400
And we will have conned them

00:10:07.400 --> 00:10:09.400
In the sense that they will come for us

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:11.400
They will miss us completely

00:10:11.400 --> 00:10:14.400
In the meantime the Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:10:14.400 --> 00:10:17.400
Who was informed that look we have seen these people

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:19.400
And you can proceed

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:22.400
The Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam began to proceed

00:10:22.400 --> 00:10:25.400
And very importantly

00:10:25.400 --> 00:10:28.400
With the Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:10:28.400 --> 00:10:31.400
As we said only 313 people

00:10:31.400 --> 00:10:34.400
After he had vetted whoever needed vetting and so on

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:38.400
And from amongst them they had only 2 horsemen

00:10:38.400 --> 00:10:40.400
Only 2 horsemen

00:10:40.400 --> 00:10:42.400
And this is something amazing

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:43.400
The 2 horsemen

00:10:43.400 --> 00:10:45.400
Az-Zubair ibn Al-Awwam radiallahu anhu

00:10:45.400 --> 00:10:48.400
And Al-Mikhdad ibn Al-Aswad radiallahu anhu

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:49.400
These were the 2 horsemen

00:10:49.400 --> 00:10:50.400
Only 2

00:10:50.400 --> 00:10:53.400
And they had 70 camels with them

00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:57.400
Which were being made use of

00:10:57.400 --> 00:10:59.400
They were sharing the camels

00:10:59.400 --> 00:11:01.400
So one would ride, two would walk

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:03.400
Then from the two who walked

00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:05.400
One would ride and the other two would walk

00:11:05.400 --> 00:11:07.400
And they continued in that way

00:11:07.400 --> 00:11:09.400
They shared it so much so

00:11:09.400 --> 00:11:11.400
That Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:11:11.400 --> 00:11:14.400
Himself also shared the camels

00:11:14.400 --> 00:11:16.400
Not that he was the leader so he just sat on one

00:11:16.400 --> 00:11:18.400
No, he sat on it after some time

00:11:18.400 --> 00:11:20.400
He gave the chance to Ali radiallahu anhu

00:11:20.400 --> 00:11:22.400
Who was with him and so on

00:11:22.400 --> 00:11:24.400
One narration says Abu Lubaba was with them

00:11:24.400 --> 00:11:27.400
And he gave the chance to Abu Lubaba and so on

00:11:27.400 --> 00:11:31.400
As for Abu Lubaba Al-Ansari

00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:35.400
When it came to a place known as Ar-Rawha

00:11:35.400 --> 00:11:38.400
Rasulullah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:41.400
Sent him back to Madina Munawwara

00:11:41.400 --> 00:11:43.400
For what reason?

00:11:43.400 --> 00:11:44.400
As follows

00:11:44.400 --> 00:11:46.400
When they were leaving Madina Munawwara

00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:48.400
The Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:11:48.400 --> 00:11:51.400
Left Abdullah ibn Ummi Maktum

00:11:51.400 --> 00:11:53.400
The blind companion radiallahu anhu

00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:55.400
In charge of Salah

00:11:55.400 --> 00:11:56.400
And in charge of Madina

00:11:56.400 --> 00:11:59.400
So he was basically responsible for what went on

00:11:59.400 --> 00:12:01.400
But as they got to Ar-Rawha

00:12:01.400 --> 00:12:03.400
The Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:12:03.400 --> 00:12:05.400
Sent back Abu Lubaba and said

00:12:05.400 --> 00:12:07.400
You will be the Ameer in Madina

00:12:07.400 --> 00:12:09.400
For as long as I am away

00:12:09.400 --> 00:12:12.400
In this particular escapade

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:13.400
Or in this journey

00:12:13.400 --> 00:12:16.400
So Abu Lubaba Al-Ansari radiallahu anhu

00:12:16.400 --> 00:12:18.400
He had gone back

00:12:18.400 --> 00:12:21.400
In fact this was Abu Lubaba ibn Abdul Munthir

00:12:21.400 --> 00:12:22.400
That was the one who went back

00:12:22.400 --> 00:12:25.400
And he was the one who was responsible

00:12:25.400 --> 00:12:27.400
In Madina Munawwara during the absence of

00:12:27.400 --> 00:12:29.400
Rasulullah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:12:29.400 --> 00:12:31.400
On that occasion

00:12:31.400 --> 00:12:33.400
Now as they had gone

00:12:33.400 --> 00:12:35.400
The Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:12:35.400 --> 00:12:38.400
Divided the army into two major divisions

00:12:38.400 --> 00:12:40.400
One was the Ansar

00:12:40.400 --> 00:12:42.400
Headed by Ali radiallahu anhu

00:12:42.400 --> 00:12:44.400
He was given a flag

00:12:44.400 --> 00:12:46.400
The color of the flag was black

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:49.400
And the other was Sa'd ibn Mu'adh

00:12:49.400 --> 00:12:50.400
On the other side

00:12:50.400 --> 00:12:52.400
Who was the leader of the Ansar

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:55.400
So Muhajireen on one side led by Ali radiallahu anhu

00:12:55.400 --> 00:12:59.400
The Ansar on the other side led by Sa'd ibn Mu'adh radiallahu anhu

00:12:59.400 --> 00:13:01.400
The two of them had black flags

00:13:01.400 --> 00:13:03.400
And as for the general flag

00:13:03.400 --> 00:13:06.400
For all the Muslims together as an entire army

00:13:06.400 --> 00:13:10.400
It was given to Mus'ab ibn Umayr radiallahu anhu

00:13:10.400 --> 00:13:12.400
And it was a white flag

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:14.400
As you know we learned yesterday

00:13:14.400 --> 00:13:16.400
That the flag for the general army was always white

00:13:16.400 --> 00:13:19.400
Why the black ones was to distinguish between

00:13:19.400 --> 00:13:22.400
The different battalions within the same army

00:13:22.400 --> 00:13:25.400
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us a deep understanding

00:13:25.400 --> 00:13:27.400
Then on the right side of the army

00:13:27.400 --> 00:13:28.400
The Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:13:28.400 --> 00:13:30.400
Put a Zubair ibn Al-Awwam

00:13:30.400 --> 00:13:32.400
Who was in the front with his horse

00:13:32.400 --> 00:13:33.400
He had a horse

00:13:33.400 --> 00:13:36.400
And on the left side he put Al-Mikhdad ibn Al-Aswad radiallahu anhu

00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:38.400
Who also had a horse

00:13:38.400 --> 00:13:41.400
So these two horsemen were placed on either side of the army

00:13:41.400 --> 00:13:44.400
And with those who were on foot

00:13:44.400 --> 00:13:45.400
The Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:13:45.400 --> 00:13:49.400
Put Qais ibn Abi Sa'd Sa'd radiallahu anhu

00:13:49.400 --> 00:13:51.400
And the army progressed slowly

00:13:51.400 --> 00:13:57.400
But surely they had with them those who would provide food and so on

00:13:57.400 --> 00:14:01.400
And they ate from amongst the camels that they had

00:14:01.400 --> 00:14:02.400
They would slaughter and so on

00:14:02.400 --> 00:14:03.400
This was the norm at the time

00:14:03.400 --> 00:14:05.400
And they slowly progressed subhanallah

00:14:05.400 --> 00:14:09.400
In the meantime you find Abu Sufyan

00:14:09.400 --> 00:14:14.400
Very very intelligently sent a message to Quraish

00:14:14.400 --> 00:14:15.400
What was the message?

00:14:15.400 --> 00:14:17.400
You see this caravan

00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:21.400
All the leaders of Quraish had had their loot in it

00:14:21.400 --> 00:14:25.400
And they had sent Abu Sufyan with it going up to Ash-Sham

00:14:25.400 --> 00:14:27.400
So he sent a message to say

00:14:27.400 --> 00:14:30.400
Your people's containers are at stake

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:32.400
I'm using today's terminology

00:14:32.400 --> 00:14:34.400
You see today you have a big container coming

00:14:34.400 --> 00:14:36.400
And when someone says there's a problem with your container

00:14:36.400 --> 00:14:39.400
Ask the business people how they cannot sleep

00:14:39.400 --> 00:14:40.400
May Allah safeguard us

00:14:40.400 --> 00:14:42.400
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:46.400
Imagine all the wealth of all these people

00:14:46.400 --> 00:14:47.400
And what happens?

00:14:47.400 --> 00:14:49.400
It is now at stake

00:14:49.400 --> 00:14:50.400
From who?

00:14:50.400 --> 00:14:53.400
From Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam and his companions

00:14:53.400 --> 00:14:55.400
But the Muslims were not looters

00:14:55.400 --> 00:14:57.400
They were not people who were oppressors

00:14:57.400 --> 00:15:00.400
They were going to get back their rightful property

00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:02.400
Which was usurped from them in Makkah

00:15:02.400 --> 00:15:04.400
We need to get the slate

00:15:04.400 --> 00:15:07.400
Sometimes on a global level the non-Muslims

00:15:07.400 --> 00:15:11.400
Make it seem like the Muslims were greedy to fight

00:15:11.400 --> 00:15:13.400
Or they really wanted all the loot and so on

00:15:13.400 --> 00:15:14.400
It wasn't the case

00:15:14.400 --> 00:15:17.400
These people were persecuted and killed for 14 years

00:15:17.400 --> 00:15:19.400
Their wealth was taken from them

00:15:19.400 --> 00:15:20.400
Everything usurped

00:15:20.400 --> 00:15:22.400
That same wealth, the property and so on

00:15:22.400 --> 00:15:25.400
Was used now in order for these people to become richer

00:15:25.400 --> 00:15:27.400
That wealth belonged to us

00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:28.400
Subhanallah

00:15:28.400 --> 00:15:30.400
Nothing wrong in going to get it

00:15:30.400 --> 00:15:32.400
Even if it means to fight in order to get it back

00:15:32.400 --> 00:15:36.400
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us a deeper understanding

00:15:36.400 --> 00:15:39.400
So the people of Quraysh

00:15:39.400 --> 00:15:41.400
They were very very upset

00:15:41.400 --> 00:15:42.400
Very angry

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:45.400
Abu Jahal and the likes made an announcement

00:15:45.400 --> 00:15:47.400
And the announcement was

00:15:47.400 --> 00:15:50.400
Come on, let's go out and protect our property

00:15:50.400 --> 00:15:51.400
Number one

00:15:51.400 --> 00:15:52.400
Number two is

00:15:52.400 --> 00:15:55.400
We can go out with so much power

00:15:55.400 --> 00:15:59.400
That we will just destroy Muhammad and his companions all at once

00:16:00.400 --> 00:16:02.400
Abu Sufyan already had had

00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:04.400
Because now he sent his spies

00:16:04.400 --> 00:16:06.400
And he found out figures

00:16:06.400 --> 00:16:07.400
He found out where they were

00:16:07.400 --> 00:16:09.400
He found out the movements and so on

00:16:09.400 --> 00:16:11.400
He knew exactly what was going on

00:16:11.400 --> 00:16:13.400
What type of weaponry these people had

00:16:13.400 --> 00:16:14.400
Where they were, what were

00:16:14.400 --> 00:16:16.400
Everything he had found out

00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:17.400
He had figured it out

00:16:17.400 --> 00:16:19.400
Because the people of Quraysh were warriors

00:16:19.400 --> 00:16:21.400
They used to fight anyway

00:16:21.400 --> 00:16:24.400
But as for Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:26.400
He was not a warrior and a fighter

00:16:26.400 --> 00:16:27.400
No

00:16:27.400 --> 00:16:30.400
He was made to go out to defend

00:16:30.400 --> 00:16:33.400
And that is when he became the best of the lot

00:16:33.400 --> 00:16:35.400
Because from Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:16:35.400 --> 00:16:36.400
Divine revelation

00:16:36.400 --> 00:16:38.400
He knew exactly what to do

00:16:38.400 --> 00:16:39.400
Sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:16:39.400 --> 00:16:43.710
So the people of Quraysh came

00:16:43.710 --> 00:16:44.710
How many of them?

00:16:44.710 --> 00:16:46.710
When they left, it is reported

00:16:46.710 --> 00:16:49.710
They were 1,300 strong men

00:16:49.710 --> 00:16:52.710
When they left Makkah

00:16:52.710 --> 00:16:53.710
The number dwindled

00:16:53.710 --> 00:16:54.710
It came down

00:16:54.710 --> 00:16:55.710
We'll explain how it came down

00:16:55.710 --> 00:16:56.710
But when they left

00:16:56.710 --> 00:16:58.710
They were strong men

00:16:58.710 --> 00:16:59.710
From amongst them

00:16:59.710 --> 00:17:01.710
They say 1,000 horses

00:17:01.710 --> 00:17:03.710
And here we only had two horses

00:17:03.710 --> 00:17:04.710
Subhanallah

00:17:04.710 --> 00:17:06.710
And they were well equipped

00:17:06.710 --> 00:17:08.710
Abu Jahl was so excited

00:17:08.710 --> 00:17:10.710
He said we will go to Badr

00:17:10.710 --> 00:17:11.710
And we will camp there

00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:12.710
Because as it is

00:17:12.710 --> 00:17:14.710
It's more like a holiday spot there

00:17:14.710 --> 00:17:16.710
We're going to take young girls and women

00:17:16.710 --> 00:17:17.710
We're going to take alcohol

00:17:17.710 --> 00:17:18.710
We'll party there

00:17:18.710 --> 00:17:19.710
We'll wait for these people

00:17:19.710 --> 00:17:20.710
When they come

00:17:20.710 --> 00:17:21.710
We will finish them up

00:17:21.710 --> 00:17:24.710
And we will sort them out

00:17:24.710 --> 00:17:25.710
They were going to have a party

00:17:25.710 --> 00:17:28.710
Because to them it was a superpower

00:17:28.710 --> 00:17:33.710
Against a force similar to the Goliath David

00:17:33.710 --> 00:17:35.710
Scenario of many years ago

00:17:35.710 --> 00:17:37.710
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:17:37.710 --> 00:17:39.710
Grant us a deeper understanding

00:17:39.710 --> 00:17:41.710
Dawood a.s.

00:17:41.710 --> 00:17:42.710
Allah says

00:17:46.710 --> 00:17:49.710
How many armies that were smaller

00:17:49.710 --> 00:17:52.710
Have overcome armies that were huge

00:17:52.710 --> 00:17:54.710
By the will of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:17:54.710 --> 00:17:56.710
So these people had gone

00:17:56.710 --> 00:17:58.710
In a great number

00:17:58.710 --> 00:18:00.710
When Abu Sufyan was safe

00:18:00.710 --> 00:18:02.710
He sent another message to Quraysh

00:18:02.710 --> 00:18:03.710
As they left

00:18:03.710 --> 00:18:04.710
What was the message?

00:18:04.710 --> 00:18:06.710
Now you people can stay

00:18:06.710 --> 00:18:07.710
And you people can go back

00:18:07.710 --> 00:18:08.710
Because we are now safe

00:18:08.710 --> 00:18:10.710
And your property is safe

00:18:10.710 --> 00:18:11.710
So it was good enough

00:18:11.710 --> 00:18:12.710
For them to say

00:18:12.710 --> 00:18:13.710
Okay, property is safe

00:18:13.710 --> 00:18:14.710
Let's go back to Mecca

00:18:14.710 --> 00:18:16.710
But no, they prepared so much

00:18:16.710 --> 00:18:17.710
They had pride

00:18:17.710 --> 00:18:18.710
They had this haughtiness

00:18:18.710 --> 00:18:20.710
We want to wipe out these Muslims

00:18:20.710 --> 00:18:22.710
And we must sort them out

00:18:22.710 --> 00:18:25.710
And Allah wanted something to come to pass

00:18:25.710 --> 00:18:26.710
As we will see

00:18:26.710 --> 00:18:27.710
So now

00:18:27.710 --> 00:18:28.710
Abu Jahl says

00:18:28.710 --> 00:18:30.710
No, we are not going to go back

00:18:30.710 --> 00:18:33.710
But a few of the people decided

00:18:33.710 --> 00:18:34.710
No, we want to go back

00:18:34.710 --> 00:18:36.710
There is no point now in fighting

00:18:36.710 --> 00:18:37.710
So if we take a look

00:18:37.710 --> 00:18:40.710
Banu Zahra, they had came back

00:18:40.710 --> 00:18:41.710
They had returned

00:18:41.710 --> 00:18:43.710
So the numbers became smaller

00:18:43.710 --> 00:18:45.710
Of the disbelievers

00:18:45.710 --> 00:18:46.710
And from the very beginning

00:18:46.710 --> 00:18:48.710
Abu Lahab was one of them

00:18:48.710 --> 00:18:49.710
Who could not go

00:18:49.710 --> 00:18:50.710
What had happened?

00:18:50.710 --> 00:18:51.710
All the leaders came out

00:18:51.710 --> 00:18:52.710
Abu Jahl came out

00:18:52.710 --> 00:18:53.710
Utba ibn Rabi'a

00:18:53.710 --> 00:18:54.710
Shayb ibn Rabi'a

00:18:54.710 --> 00:18:56.710
A lot of these top people

00:18:56.710 --> 00:18:57.710
Umayyah ibn Khalaf

00:18:57.710 --> 00:18:58.710
All of them came out

00:18:58.710 --> 00:18:59.710
The leaders of Quraysh

00:18:59.710 --> 00:19:00.710
Because they were so excited

00:19:00.710 --> 00:19:02.710
We're going to wipe out the Muslims

00:19:02.710 --> 00:19:03.710
And those who could not make it

00:19:03.710 --> 00:19:05.710
They sent their family members

00:19:05.710 --> 00:19:06.710
And kith and kin

00:19:06.710 --> 00:19:07.710
To come out on their behalf

00:19:07.710 --> 00:19:08.710
Such as Abu Lahab

00:19:08.710 --> 00:19:10.710
He couldn't make it on his own

00:19:10.710 --> 00:19:12.710
And Abu Lahab fell very sick

00:19:12.710 --> 00:19:13.710
At some stage

00:19:13.710 --> 00:19:16.710
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us a lesson

00:19:16.710 --> 00:19:18.710
He was the one who used to throw

00:19:18.710 --> 00:19:20.710
Astaghfirullah

00:19:20.710 --> 00:19:23.710
Dirt upon Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:19:23.710 --> 00:19:24.710
He lost his health

00:19:24.710 --> 00:19:27.710
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala safeguard us

00:19:27.710 --> 00:19:28.710
Really

00:19:28.710 --> 00:19:29.710
We ask Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:19:29.710 --> 00:19:30.710
To grant us purity

00:19:30.710 --> 00:19:32.710
And to make us not from amongst

00:19:32.710 --> 00:19:34.710
Those who blaspheme

00:19:34.710 --> 00:19:35.710
To make us not from amongst

00:19:35.710 --> 00:19:36.710
Those who earn the wrath

00:19:36.710 --> 00:19:37.710
Of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:19:37.710 --> 00:19:38.710
We are fortunate

00:19:38.710 --> 00:19:41.710
That knowledge is very easy nowadays

00:19:41.710 --> 00:19:42.710
It's at our fingertips

00:19:42.710 --> 00:19:44.710
It's not difficult to learn

00:19:44.710 --> 00:19:46.710
As it was many many years ago

00:19:46.710 --> 00:19:49.710
Because today we have access

00:19:49.710 --> 00:19:50.710
Not only to the internet

00:19:50.710 --> 00:19:51.710
But to people

00:19:51.710 --> 00:19:53.710
If you want someone

00:19:53.710 --> 00:19:54.710
To speak to them live

00:19:54.710 --> 00:19:55.710
You don't need to travel

00:19:55.710 --> 00:19:57.710
For 8 days and 16 days

00:19:57.710 --> 00:19:59.710
You can pick up a telephone today

00:19:59.710 --> 00:20:01.710
You can fly in 8 hours

00:20:01.710 --> 00:20:03.710
And you can get to anyone on the globe

00:20:03.710 --> 00:20:04.710
To find out

00:20:04.710 --> 00:20:05.710
Still we are lazy

00:20:05.710 --> 00:20:06.710
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:20:06.710 --> 00:20:08.710
Help us earn the knowledge of deen

00:20:08.710 --> 00:20:09.710
And may He make us from those

00:20:09.710 --> 00:20:10.710
Who understand and realize

00:20:10.710 --> 00:20:13.710
Through the Sunnah of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:20:13.710 --> 00:20:15.710
So Abu Lahab he didn't come

00:20:15.710 --> 00:20:17.710
And there was a clan

00:20:17.710 --> 00:20:19.710
That did not attend at all

00:20:19.710 --> 00:20:20.710
Banu Adi

00:20:20.710 --> 00:20:21.710
They just refused

00:20:21.710 --> 00:20:22.710
They said look we are not interested

00:20:22.710 --> 00:20:23.710
In fighting from the very beginning

00:20:23.710 --> 00:20:24.710
So now

00:20:24.710 --> 00:20:26.710
Banu Adi was behind in Mecca

00:20:26.710 --> 00:20:28.710
Abu Lahab was behind in Mecca

00:20:28.710 --> 00:20:29.710
And now Banu Zuhra

00:20:29.710 --> 00:20:30.710
They decided to go back

00:20:30.710 --> 00:20:32.710
After Abu Sufyan sent the second note

00:20:32.710 --> 00:20:33.710
And the second letter

00:20:33.710 --> 00:20:35.710
However

00:20:35.710 --> 00:20:38.710
When Quraysh got close to Badr

00:20:38.710 --> 00:20:40.710
They were insisting on war

00:20:40.710 --> 00:20:41.710
We want to fight these people

00:20:41.710 --> 00:20:43.710
Now it's no longer about the caravan

00:20:43.710 --> 00:20:44.710
The caravan is gone

00:20:44.710 --> 00:20:45.710
It's passed

00:20:45.710 --> 00:20:46.710
It's safe

00:20:46.710 --> 00:20:47.710
Now it's about these people

00:20:47.710 --> 00:20:48.710
We want to fight them

00:20:48.710 --> 00:20:50.710
Now Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:20:50.710 --> 00:20:51.710
Did not want to fight

00:20:51.710 --> 00:20:53.710
When he came out of Mecca

00:20:53.710 --> 00:20:55.710
Of Madinah Munawwara

00:20:55.710 --> 00:20:56.710
He intended the caravan

00:20:56.710 --> 00:20:58.710
He did not intend

00:20:58.710 --> 00:20:59.710
A war

00:20:59.710 --> 00:21:01.710
So what he did is

00:21:01.710 --> 00:21:02.710
He started asking

00:21:02.710 --> 00:21:04.710
The opinion of his companions

00:21:04.710 --> 00:21:05.710
What do you think?

00:21:05.710 --> 00:21:07.710
Should we fight these people?

00:21:07.710 --> 00:21:09.710
And obviously there were two opinions

00:21:09.710 --> 00:21:10.710
Because

00:21:10.710 --> 00:21:12.710
Those who said we should not fight them

00:21:12.710 --> 00:21:14.710
They were only concerned that

00:21:14.710 --> 00:21:16.710
Look we are not heavily armed

00:21:16.710 --> 00:21:19.710
We came out with just a few weapons

00:21:19.710 --> 00:21:21.710
Each one of us has a sword

00:21:21.710 --> 00:21:24.710
We have a limited number of bows and arrows

00:21:24.710 --> 00:21:25.710
And at the same time

00:21:25.710 --> 00:21:26.710
We came for a caravan

00:21:26.710 --> 00:21:27.710
Which had in it

00:21:27.710 --> 00:21:29.710
Just a few people

00:21:29.710 --> 00:21:31.710
And now we are going to face

00:21:31.710 --> 00:21:32.710
The super power of the time

00:21:32.710 --> 00:21:34.710
And we are so small in number

00:21:34.710 --> 00:21:36.710
So it's not like they wanted to run away

00:21:36.710 --> 00:21:38.710
But they were putting forward a case to say

00:21:38.710 --> 00:21:40.710
It's not going to be worth it fighting

00:21:40.710 --> 00:21:42.710
However, subhanallah

00:21:42.710 --> 00:21:44.710
Listen to what Al-Miqdad ibn al-Aswad

00:21:44.710 --> 00:21:46.710
Radhiallahu anhu says

00:21:46.710 --> 00:21:48.710
He was one of the men on the horse

00:21:48.710 --> 00:21:50.710
When the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:21:50.710 --> 00:21:51.710
Said

00:21:51.710 --> 00:21:53.710
Should we go and fight these people or not?

00:21:53.710 --> 00:21:54.710
He says

00:21:54.710 --> 00:21:56.710
He says O messenger sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:21:56.710 --> 00:21:59.710
We are not going to give you the answer

00:21:59.710 --> 00:22:01.710
That Banu Israel gave the Prophet Moses

00:22:01.710 --> 00:22:03.710
Musa alayhi sallatu wasallam

00:22:03.710 --> 00:22:04.710
When they told him

00:22:12.710 --> 00:22:14.710
Go you and your Rabb and go and fight

00:22:14.710 --> 00:22:15.710
We are sitting and waiting here

00:22:15.710 --> 00:22:17.710
We are going to say

00:22:17.710 --> 00:22:19.710
We will come with you and we will fight

00:22:19.710 --> 00:22:20.710
The decision is yours

00:22:20.710 --> 00:22:21.710
You make a decision

00:22:21.710 --> 00:22:22.710
We are with you

00:22:22.710 --> 00:22:23.710
Subhanallah

00:22:24.710 --> 00:22:25.710
So this was the difference

00:22:25.710 --> 00:22:27.710
The companions of the Prophet

00:22:27.710 --> 00:22:28.710
Musa alayhi sallatu wasallam

00:22:28.710 --> 00:22:29.710
They told him

00:22:29.710 --> 00:22:30.710
You go and fight

00:22:30.710 --> 00:22:31.710
We are waiting here

00:22:31.710 --> 00:22:33.710
We don't want to tackle these Jababirah

00:22:33.710 --> 00:22:35.710
And these tyrants

00:22:35.710 --> 00:22:36.710
You and your Lord

00:22:36.710 --> 00:22:37.710
The two of you can go

00:22:37.710 --> 00:22:38.710
I seek refuge with Allah

00:22:38.710 --> 00:22:40.710
So Al-Miqdad ibn al-Aswad says

00:22:40.710 --> 00:22:42.710
We will not say that

00:22:42.710 --> 00:22:43.710
We are going to say

00:22:43.710 --> 00:22:44.710
The decision is yours

00:22:44.710 --> 00:22:45.710
We are with you

00:22:45.710 --> 00:22:47.710
Go and we are right behind you

00:22:47.710 --> 00:22:48.710
Subhanallah

00:22:48.710 --> 00:22:50.710
Then the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:22:50.710 --> 00:22:51.710
Turns to the Ansar

00:22:51.710 --> 00:22:53.710
Why did he turn to the Ansar?

00:22:53.710 --> 00:22:55.710
It's important to seek the opinion

00:22:55.710 --> 00:22:57.710
Of those who are warriors

00:22:57.710 --> 00:22:58.710
Those who are going to fight

00:22:58.710 --> 00:23:00.710
If we want to engage in a war

00:23:00.710 --> 00:23:01.710
You need their opinion

00:23:01.710 --> 00:23:02.710
Not like today

00:23:02.710 --> 00:23:03.710
Man makes a decision

00:23:03.710 --> 00:23:04.710
The people on the ground

00:23:04.710 --> 00:23:06.710
Have no say whatsoever

00:23:06.710 --> 00:23:07.710
Half of them are so innocent

00:23:07.710 --> 00:23:08.710
They don't even know why

00:23:08.710 --> 00:23:10.710
Like the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam says

00:23:10.710 --> 00:23:12.710
There will come a time

00:23:16.710 --> 00:23:17.710
There will come a time

00:23:17.710 --> 00:23:19.710
When the killer doesn't know

00:23:19.710 --> 00:23:20.710
Why he is killing

00:23:20.710 --> 00:23:21.710
And the one who is murdered

00:23:21.710 --> 00:23:23.710
Won't know why he was murdered

00:23:23.710 --> 00:23:24.710
Go and ask the army

00:23:24.710 --> 00:23:26.710
Is doing their rounds on the globe

00:23:26.710 --> 00:23:27.710
Why are you doing this?

00:23:27.710 --> 00:23:28.710
They say I don't know

00:23:28.710 --> 00:23:29.710
We don't know

00:23:29.710 --> 00:23:30.710
And ask the people who are killed

00:23:30.710 --> 00:23:31.710
Why are you being killed?

00:23:31.710 --> 00:23:32.710
They say we don't know

00:23:32.710 --> 00:23:33.710
We don't know

00:23:33.710 --> 00:23:34.710
That is a prophecy of

00:23:34.710 --> 00:23:35.710
Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:23:35.710 --> 00:23:37.710
He said a time will come

00:23:37.710 --> 00:23:38.710
When people won't even know

00:23:38.710 --> 00:23:39.710
Why they are doing

00:23:39.710 --> 00:23:40.710
What they are doing

00:23:40.710 --> 00:23:41.710
But they will be spreading

00:23:41.710 --> 00:23:42.710
Corruption across the earth

00:23:42.710 --> 00:23:44.710
May Allah safeguard us

00:23:44.710 --> 00:23:45.710
As for the Muslims

00:23:45.710 --> 00:23:46.710
They sought the opinion

00:23:46.710 --> 00:23:47.710
Of one another

00:23:47.710 --> 00:23:49.710
Even Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:23:49.710 --> 00:23:51.710
Although the instruction was his

00:23:51.710 --> 00:23:53.710
And Allah had already revealed to him

00:23:53.710 --> 00:23:55.710
But in order for us all

00:23:55.710 --> 00:23:56.710
To learn a lesson

00:23:56.710 --> 00:23:59.710
As to the importance of seeking opinion

00:23:59.710 --> 00:24:01.710
He asked the Muhajireen

00:24:01.710 --> 00:24:03.710
And he asked the Ansar

00:24:03.710 --> 00:24:04.710
As for the Ansar

00:24:04.710 --> 00:24:06.710
It was because he had a treaty with them

00:24:06.710 --> 00:24:08.710
To protect him in Medina

00:24:08.710 --> 00:24:10.710
But he didn't have a treaty with them

00:24:10.710 --> 00:24:11.710
That they would protect him

00:24:11.710 --> 00:24:13.710
Else way outside of Medina Munawwara

00:24:13.710 --> 00:24:15.710
It was important that he asked them the question

00:24:15.710 --> 00:24:18.710
Look, we are now heading for Badr

00:24:18.710 --> 00:24:20.710
Is it possible that you people

00:24:20.710 --> 00:24:21.710
Would like to fight with us?

00:24:21.710 --> 00:24:23.710
And Sa'd ibn Mu'adh

00:24:23.710 --> 00:24:24.710
The head of Al-Aws

00:24:24.710 --> 00:24:26.710
We mentioned his name so many times

00:24:26.710 --> 00:24:27.710
The one who accepted Islam

00:24:27.710 --> 00:24:29.710
At the hands of Mus'ab ibn Umayr

00:24:29.710 --> 00:24:30.710
Radhiallahu anhu

00:24:30.710 --> 00:24:32.710
Sa'd ibn Mu'adh says

00:24:32.710 --> 00:24:34.710
Ya Rasulallah sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:24:34.710 --> 00:24:36.710
You came to us

00:24:36.710 --> 00:24:37.710
We believed in you

00:24:37.710 --> 00:24:38.710
We believe you are the messenger

00:24:38.710 --> 00:24:40.710
We believe you are our leader

00:24:40.710 --> 00:24:42.710
We have obeyed your instructions

00:24:42.710 --> 00:24:44.710
We will continue obeying your instructions

00:24:44.710 --> 00:24:45.710
You tell us what to do

00:24:45.710 --> 00:24:46.710
Even if you take us

00:24:46.710 --> 00:24:48.710
And instruct us to dive into the ocean

00:24:48.710 --> 00:24:49.710
We will dive straight after you

00:24:49.710 --> 00:24:50.710
Subhanallah

00:24:50.710 --> 00:24:51.710
Tell us whatever you want

00:24:51.710 --> 00:24:52.710
We are with you

00:24:52.710 --> 00:24:53.710
So what happened?

00:24:53.710 --> 00:24:55.710
That gave strength to the rest of them

00:24:55.710 --> 00:24:57.710
And Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:24:57.710 --> 00:24:59.710
Speaks about this in the Quran

00:24:59.710 --> 00:25:00.710
And Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:25:00.710 --> 00:25:02.710
Speaks about how

00:25:02.710 --> 00:25:04.710
It would have been good

00:25:04.710 --> 00:25:06.710
If the Muslims had had the caravan

00:25:06.710 --> 00:25:08.710
Which was the easier one

00:25:08.710 --> 00:25:09.710
But Allah says

00:25:09.710 --> 00:25:11.710
We wanted something to happen

00:25:11.710 --> 00:25:13.710
And Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:25:13.710 --> 00:25:14.710
Speaks about this

00:25:14.710 --> 00:25:15.710
Subhanallah

00:25:15.710 --> 00:25:16.710
Speaks about this

00:25:16.710 --> 00:25:17.710
So beautifully

00:25:17.710 --> 00:25:19.710
And Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:25:19.710 --> 00:25:20.710
Tells us how

00:25:20.710 --> 00:25:22.710
Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:25:22.710 --> 00:25:23.710
Was favored

00:25:23.710 --> 00:25:25.710
And Allah says

00:25:31.710 --> 00:25:33.710
All this was in order

00:25:33.710 --> 00:25:35.710
For Allah to make

00:25:35.710 --> 00:25:36.710
To pass

00:25:36.710 --> 00:25:38.710
That which was meant

00:25:38.710 --> 00:25:40.710
To come to pass

00:25:40.710 --> 00:25:41.710
Subhanallah

00:25:41.710 --> 00:25:42.710
Allah says

00:25:44.710 --> 00:25:49.710
The beginning of that verse

00:25:49.710 --> 00:26:13.710
Arabic

00:26:13.710 --> 00:26:15.710
When Allah had promised you

00:26:15.710 --> 00:26:17.710
That you will definitely be victorious

00:26:18.710 --> 00:26:20.710
Over one of the two armies

00:26:20.710 --> 00:26:21.710
You had intended

00:26:21.710 --> 00:26:22.710
You had hoped

00:26:22.710 --> 00:26:24.710
That the easier one be yours

00:26:24.710 --> 00:26:25.710
Which means those

00:26:25.710 --> 00:26:26.710
Who were with the caravan

00:26:26.710 --> 00:26:27.710
Small in number

00:26:27.710 --> 00:26:28.710
You were hoping

00:26:28.710 --> 00:26:29.710
That that would have been the one

00:26:29.710 --> 00:26:31.710
That Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:26:31.710 --> 00:26:32.710
Had meant

00:26:32.710 --> 00:26:33.710
When He promised you

00:26:33.710 --> 00:26:34.710
One of the two

00:26:34.710 --> 00:26:35.710
But Allah says

00:26:35.710 --> 00:26:37.710
But Allah intended for you

00:26:37.710 --> 00:26:38.710
To go for the big one

00:26:38.710 --> 00:26:41.710
Because He wanted to cut off

00:26:41.710 --> 00:26:43.710
The backs of the disbelievers

00:26:43.710 --> 00:26:44.710
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:26:44.710 --> 00:26:46.710
Protect us

00:26:46.710 --> 00:26:47.710
Amazing

00:26:47.710 --> 00:26:49.710
So this was Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:26:49.710 --> 00:26:50.710
And this is why

00:26:50.710 --> 00:26:51.710
Allah says

00:27:03.710 --> 00:27:05.710
Just as Allah removed you

00:27:05.710 --> 00:27:07.710
From your house in Medina

00:27:07.710 --> 00:27:08.710
To go out

00:27:08.710 --> 00:27:09.710
Allah is the one

00:27:09.710 --> 00:27:10.710
Who took them out

00:27:10.710 --> 00:27:12.710
To go to the battle of Badr

00:27:12.710 --> 00:27:14.710
And Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:27:14.710 --> 00:27:15.710
And then you found

00:27:15.710 --> 00:27:16.710
That some of the believers

00:27:16.710 --> 00:27:18.710
Were not really willing to fight

00:27:18.710 --> 00:27:19.710
When?

00:27:19.710 --> 00:27:20.710
When they were asked

00:27:20.710 --> 00:27:21.710
Do you now want to fight

00:27:21.710 --> 00:27:22.710
Or go back?

00:27:22.710 --> 00:27:23.710
As I told you

00:27:23.710 --> 00:27:24.710
There were two opinions

00:27:24.710 --> 00:27:25.710
They did not say

00:27:25.710 --> 00:27:26.710
We are not willing to fight

00:27:26.710 --> 00:27:27.710
Because they didn't want

00:27:27.710 --> 00:27:29.710
To obey the instruction

00:27:29.710 --> 00:27:30.710
If the instruction came

00:27:30.710 --> 00:27:31.710
They would obey

00:27:31.710 --> 00:27:32.710
But they were asked

00:27:32.710 --> 00:27:33.710
For their opinion

00:27:33.710 --> 00:27:34.710
And all they said is

00:27:34.710 --> 00:27:35.710
We don't think it's a good idea

00:27:35.710 --> 00:27:36.710
Because we are not

00:27:36.710 --> 00:27:39.710
As well equipped as the others

00:27:39.710 --> 00:27:41.710
So Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:27:45.710 --> 00:27:46.710
They are arguing with you

00:27:46.710 --> 00:27:47.710
About the truth

00:27:47.710 --> 00:27:49.710
After it is made clear to them

00:27:49.710 --> 00:27:50.710
As though

00:27:50.710 --> 00:27:51.710
They are being driven

00:27:51.710 --> 00:27:52.710
To their death

00:27:52.710 --> 00:27:54.710
Whilst they are watching

00:27:54.710 --> 00:27:56.710
Look at the words of the Quran

00:27:56.710 --> 00:27:58.710
Nobody is driving anyone

00:27:58.710 --> 00:28:00.710
To their death

00:28:00.710 --> 00:28:02.710
But it's Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:28:02.710 --> 00:28:04.710
They came after that

00:28:04.710 --> 00:28:05.710
The instruction of Allah

00:28:05.710 --> 00:28:07.710
To put them in the battle

00:28:07.710 --> 00:28:09.710
And Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:28:09.710 --> 00:28:10.710
Said

00:28:10.710 --> 00:28:12.710
And Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:28:12.710 --> 00:28:13.710
Said

00:28:13.710 --> 00:28:14.710
The instruction of Allah

00:28:14.710 --> 00:28:16.710
To proceed to badr

00:28:16.710 --> 00:28:17.710
Everything was over

00:28:17.710 --> 00:28:18.710
Allahu Akbar

00:28:18.710 --> 00:28:20.710
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:28:20.710 --> 00:28:21.710
Grant us goodness

00:28:21.710 --> 00:28:22.710
All of them proceeded

00:28:22.710 --> 00:28:23.710
Unlike the disbelievers

00:28:23.710 --> 00:28:24.710
When the letter came

00:28:24.710 --> 00:28:26.710
Some of them went back

00:28:26.710 --> 00:28:27.710
With the mu'mineen

00:28:27.710 --> 00:28:28.710
When the instruction came

00:28:28.710 --> 00:28:30.710
313 of them

00:28:30.710 --> 00:28:31.710
They arrived

00:28:31.710 --> 00:28:32.710
And they marched

00:28:32.710 --> 00:28:34.710
With Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:28:34.710 --> 00:28:37.710
So Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:28:37.710 --> 00:28:38.710
When he got there

00:28:38.710 --> 00:28:40.710
And as we made mention of

00:28:40.710 --> 00:28:41.710
What happened

00:28:41.710 --> 00:28:42.710
With Sa'd ibn Mu'adh

00:28:42.710 --> 00:28:43.710
And Al-Muqdad ibn Al-Aswad

00:28:43.710 --> 00:28:44.710
R.A.

00:28:44.710 --> 00:28:46.710
Giving the backup

00:28:46.710 --> 00:28:47.710
And making statements

00:28:47.710 --> 00:28:49.710
That really empowered everyone

00:28:49.710 --> 00:28:50.710
And made them feel

00:28:50.710 --> 00:28:52.710
Very high in moral

00:28:52.710 --> 00:28:53.710
Because obviously

00:28:53.710 --> 00:28:54.710
When your leaders are saying

00:28:54.710 --> 00:28:55.710
Let's go

00:28:55.710 --> 00:28:56.710
Everyone else who is

00:28:56.710 --> 00:28:58.710
Lower down feels very high

00:28:58.710 --> 00:28:59.710
But if the leaders were slack

00:28:59.710 --> 00:29:00.710
And saying no

00:29:00.710 --> 00:29:01.710
We're not really so much for it

00:29:01.710 --> 00:29:02.710
You find the little ones

00:29:02.710 --> 00:29:04.710
They won't even want to take part

00:29:04.710 --> 00:29:05.710
Not to say there were anyone

00:29:05.710 --> 00:29:07.710
Who was actually little

00:29:07.710 --> 00:29:09.710
But in comparison to the leaders

00:29:09.710 --> 00:29:10.710
And the leadership

00:29:10.710 --> 00:29:11.710
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:29:11.710 --> 00:29:12.710
Grant us goodness

00:29:12.710 --> 00:29:14.710
Now the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:29:14.710 --> 00:29:16.710
When he got to a certain point

00:29:16.710 --> 00:29:18.710
The army camp

00:29:18.710 --> 00:29:19.710
And when the army camp

00:29:19.710 --> 00:29:21.710
He took Abu Bakr al-Siddiq

00:29:21.710 --> 00:29:22.710
R.A.

00:29:22.710 --> 00:29:23.710
And he said

00:29:23.710 --> 00:29:24.710
Let's go and find out now

00:29:24.710 --> 00:29:25.710
We need to know

00:29:25.710 --> 00:29:26.710
The numbers of these people

00:29:26.710 --> 00:29:27.710
What type of weapons they have

00:29:27.710 --> 00:29:28.710
And so on

00:29:28.710 --> 00:29:31.710
So what happened is

00:29:31.710 --> 00:29:32.710
They hadn't even known

00:29:32.710 --> 00:29:34.710
Exactly where Quraish was

00:29:34.710 --> 00:29:38.280
They saw a man

00:29:38.280 --> 00:29:39.280
Just the two of them

00:29:39.280 --> 00:29:40.280
As they moved

00:29:40.280 --> 00:29:41.280
They went into the desert

00:29:41.280 --> 00:29:42.280
On their own

00:29:42.280 --> 00:29:43.280
They saw an old

00:29:43.280 --> 00:29:45.280
Arab Bedouin man

00:29:45.280 --> 00:29:46.280
And they told him

00:29:46.280 --> 00:29:48.280
Where are the Muslims?

00:29:48.280 --> 00:29:49.280
Good question

00:29:49.280 --> 00:29:50.280
Look at how the question is asked

00:29:50.280 --> 00:29:52.280
This is actually now

00:29:52.280 --> 00:29:53.280
A tactic

00:29:53.280 --> 00:29:54.280
To get news

00:29:54.280 --> 00:29:55.280
To get information

00:29:55.280 --> 00:29:57.280
Because now this is a war situation

00:29:57.280 --> 00:29:58.280
Where are the Muslims?

00:29:58.280 --> 00:30:00.280
He says who are you?

00:30:00.280 --> 00:30:01.280
So they said

00:30:01.280 --> 00:30:02.280
You tell us

00:30:02.280 --> 00:30:03.280
Where the Muslims are

00:30:03.280 --> 00:30:06.280
Then we tell you who we are

00:30:06.280 --> 00:30:08.280
So he says okay

00:30:08.280 --> 00:30:09.280
No he didn't say

00:30:09.280 --> 00:30:10.280
Who are you

00:30:10.280 --> 00:30:11.280
He said

00:30:11.280 --> 00:30:12.280
Where are you from?

00:30:12.280 --> 00:30:13.280
That was the question

00:30:13.280 --> 00:30:14.280
Where are you from?

00:30:14.280 --> 00:30:15.280
So they said

00:30:15.280 --> 00:30:16.280
You tell us

00:30:16.280 --> 00:30:17.280
What we want to know

00:30:17.280 --> 00:30:18.280
Then we tell you

00:30:18.280 --> 00:30:19.280
What you want to know

00:30:19.280 --> 00:30:21.280
So he says

00:30:21.280 --> 00:30:22.280
Okay the Muslims

00:30:22.280 --> 00:30:24.280
They left

00:30:24.280 --> 00:30:26.280
Medina on such and such a day

00:30:26.280 --> 00:30:28.280
There were so many of them

00:30:28.280 --> 00:30:30.280
And they headed to a certain place

00:30:30.280 --> 00:30:32.280
They were seen in this place

00:30:32.280 --> 00:30:33.280
On this day

00:30:33.280 --> 00:30:35.280
And today as we speak

00:30:35.280 --> 00:30:37.280
They should be in this place

00:30:37.280 --> 00:30:38.280
And it was so accurate

00:30:38.280 --> 00:30:39.280
Subhanallah

00:30:39.280 --> 00:30:40.280
So accurate

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:41.280
Shocking

00:30:41.280 --> 00:30:42.280
So then they said

00:30:42.280 --> 00:30:43.280
Oh

00:30:43.280 --> 00:30:44.280
Is that the case

00:30:44.280 --> 00:30:45.280
Okay

00:30:45.280 --> 00:30:47.280
What about the Makkans?

00:30:47.280 --> 00:30:48.280
Where are they?

00:30:48.280 --> 00:30:49.280
The people of Makkah

00:30:49.280 --> 00:30:50.280
Quraish

00:30:50.280 --> 00:30:51.280
He said as for Quraish

00:30:51.280 --> 00:30:52.280
They got the news

00:30:52.280 --> 00:30:54.280
And this is how they prepared

00:30:54.280 --> 00:30:55.280
They went there

00:30:55.280 --> 00:30:56.280
They went there

00:30:56.280 --> 00:30:57.280
They did this

00:30:57.280 --> 00:30:58.280
The army

00:30:58.280 --> 00:30:59.280
They should be at this place

00:30:59.280 --> 00:31:00.280
Right now

00:31:00.280 --> 00:31:01.280
Which was not very far

00:31:01.280 --> 00:31:02.280
At all

00:31:02.280 --> 00:31:03.280
So then they said

00:31:03.280 --> 00:31:04.280
He said right

00:31:04.280 --> 00:31:05.280
Now where are you from?

00:31:05.280 --> 00:31:06.280
So the Prophet

00:31:06.280 --> 00:31:07.280
Sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:31:07.280 --> 00:31:08.280
Looks at him and says

00:31:08.280 --> 00:31:09.280
We are from water

00:31:09.280 --> 00:31:10.280
And they walked away

00:31:10.280 --> 00:31:12.280
Quickly the two of them went away

00:31:12.280 --> 00:31:13.280
Now

00:31:13.280 --> 00:31:14.280
We are all from water

00:31:14.280 --> 00:31:15.280
We were created from water

00:31:15.280 --> 00:31:16.280
And dust

00:31:16.280 --> 00:31:17.280
Which was mixed together

00:31:17.280 --> 00:31:18.280
And it became clay

00:31:18.280 --> 00:31:19.280
So

00:31:19.280 --> 00:31:20.280
Because he said

00:31:20.280 --> 00:31:21.280
Where are you from?

00:31:21.280 --> 00:31:22.280
He says

00:31:22.280 --> 00:31:23.280
We are from water

00:31:23.280 --> 00:31:24.280
So Rasulullah

00:31:24.280 --> 00:31:25.280
Sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:31:25.280 --> 00:31:26.280
Went away immediately

00:31:26.280 --> 00:31:27.280
So that no further questions

00:31:27.280 --> 00:31:28.280
Would be asked

00:31:28.280 --> 00:31:29.280
And he says

00:31:29.280 --> 00:31:30.280
Which water?

00:31:30.280 --> 00:31:31.280
The water of Iraq

00:31:31.280 --> 00:31:32.280
They didn't answer anything

00:31:32.280 --> 00:31:33.280
They just carried on

00:31:33.280 --> 00:31:34.280
Because if they waited

00:31:34.280 --> 00:31:37.280
A lie would have been necessitated

00:31:37.280 --> 00:31:38.280
And if someone lied

00:31:38.280 --> 00:31:39.280
Because of war

00:31:39.280 --> 00:31:40.280
It wasn't wrong

00:31:40.280 --> 00:31:41.280
It's not wrong in the Sharia

00:31:41.280 --> 00:31:42.280
If it's a war

00:31:42.280 --> 00:31:43.280
Then subhanallah

00:31:43.280 --> 00:31:44.280
You don't need to give

00:31:44.280 --> 00:31:45.280
Your enemy the information

00:31:45.280 --> 00:31:46.280
But they knew

00:31:46.280 --> 00:31:47.280
That if we are going

00:31:47.280 --> 00:31:48.280
To tell him anything

00:31:48.280 --> 00:31:49.280
Besides this

00:31:49.280 --> 00:31:50.280
There's going to be a problem

00:31:50.280 --> 00:31:51.280
So subhanallah

00:31:51.280 --> 00:31:52.280
They went away

00:31:52.280 --> 00:31:53.280
And they found out

00:31:53.280 --> 00:31:54.280
Rasulullah Sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:31:54.280 --> 00:31:55.280
Had one powerful habit

00:31:55.280 --> 00:31:57.280
He never ever got people

00:31:57.280 --> 00:31:58.280
Worried and excited

00:31:58.280 --> 00:31:59.280
Not once

00:31:59.280 --> 00:32:00.280
He knew the news

00:32:00.280 --> 00:32:01.280
He knew how serious

00:32:01.280 --> 00:32:02.280
Everything was

00:32:02.280 --> 00:32:03.280
But he always

00:32:03.280 --> 00:32:04.280
Calmed the people down

00:32:04.280 --> 00:32:05.280
Subhanallah

00:32:05.280 --> 00:32:06.280
Unlike today

00:32:06.280 --> 00:32:08.280
We hear something minute

